{"tid":2006794,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"全球瘋玩她的「腿」 Lalisa逆天長腿走向國際因梗圖","createTime":"2020-05-08T04:27:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-08T04:33:02.000Z","uid":44730,"like":4,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"dfbc8bc4b06f12c4e8704a15c27912db329f315f","tid":2006794,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T04:27:47.000Z","msg":"有著一雙長腿還有超強舞姿，身高167公分的她跳起舞來震撼力十足，更是演藝圈公認的「舞蹈機器」。她也因為對舞蹈的熱情還有實力被選為大陸女團真人show《青春有你2》的舞蹈老師，甫登場就以短短兩分鐘的熱舞震攝全場，但在當起導師時又非常嚴厲，同時有軟萌、嚴厲的反差特質也圈了不少粉絲。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2020/05/06/99/7836789.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=750\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2020%2F05%2F06%2F99%2F7836789.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D750&h=0c43c7d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2020/05/06/99/7836790.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=750\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2020%2F05%2F06%2F99%2F7836790.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D750&h=7823cb0b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3aac2b0efcd3d545611a0144790c2abdceb33905","tid":2006794,"uid":44730,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T04:27:58.000Z","msg":"在回歸前，Lalisa也沒閒著，她在4月20日於自己的YouTube頻道上傳一支新的舞蹈影片，由編舞家Cheshir指導。不到一天觀看次數突破70幾萬，經過兩個禮拜的時間則突破140萬次觀看，可見人氣非同小可。但也正是因為這支影片，引起了全球的P圖大戰，許多網友因為Lalisa在跳舞中的腿實在太性感，紛紛P在卡通人物、電影角色身上，並寫下「Did it work?」，就連歐美大咖也來參戰！"},{"pid":"236669bf47ffc8e750a2fe97a62111ab1fe6f934","tid":2006794,"uid":44730,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T04:28:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/je_R3gEtDbw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fje_R3gEtDbw&d=kJsi%2B77Adq7yP7dZlTZe0GaNvfBTe1ydx6p2nKz01sw%3D&h=97a21b34\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/je_R3gEtDbw</a><br />\n<br />\n歐美明星舉凡詹姆斯柯登、路克伊凡斯、桃莉芭頓等人紛紛將自己上半身側躺的畫面P上Lalisa的大長腿，成功逗得網友哈哈大笑。Netflix、Fox也跟上這股風潮，將自家節目中的人物也P上她的腿，引起一陣熱議，也順勢宣傳了旗下的節目。"},{"pid":"08e5a2b0fb5ebfb57971a2d7a6aad296ca55f3bf","tid":2006794,"uid":44730,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T04:28:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2020/05/06/99/7836757.png&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=750\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2020%2F05%2F06%2F99%2F7836757.png%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D750&h=bfecaa6d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9ba9f7e05c060f5bf63dedcbd1eedd82ff22e0a6","tid":2006794,"uid":44730,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T04:28:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2020/05/06/99/7836765.png&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=750\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2020%2F05%2F06%2F99%2F7836765.png%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D750&h=ac174b13&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b0c3a0116c7459fcb123d86ab619c99f34976fd6","tid":2006794,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T04:28:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2020/05/06/99/7836768.png&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=750\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2020%2F05%2F06%2F99%2F7836768.png%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D750&h=cd4eb12c&s={SIZE}\